<br>
First trip to North Ro showed what happened if you don't pacify.  Well, I think everyone in the group will agree it's a learning experience.<br>
<br>
Level restrictions...  ohhh, as much as I hate them (I'm 56th, so I can't go into the dungeon with my friends who have storemed ahead to 65th) I suspect it is to make the job of balancing the dungeons possible.  I'd like it to be expanded to a ten-level range.... but that's purely for the selfish reason that it would let me group with the 65th'ers *now*.  Maybe I just need to make a run for 58th season.<br>
<br>
